title: Belgrade Jazz Trio
text:
The Belgrade Jazz Trio (Serbian: Beogradski džez trio) was a jazz trio founded in Belgrade, Serbia, then Yugoslavia.
Its members were Milenko Stefanović - clarinet, Vojislav Đonović - guitar and Aleksandar Nećak - bass.
